<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Posts on CJ's Blog</title><link>https://yangcj.cc/post/</link><description>Recent content in Posts on CJ's Blog</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>en-us</language><copyright>Ching Jen Yang</copyright><lastBuildDate>Sat, 28 Feb 2026 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://yangcj.cc/post/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Lunar New Year in 2026</title><link>https://yangcj.cc/p/lunar-new-year-in-2026/</link><pubDate>Sat, 28 Feb 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://yangcj.cc/p/lunar-new-year-in-2026/</guid><description>&lt;img src="https://yangcj.cc/p/lunar-new-year-in-2026/banner.jpg" alt="Featured image of post Lunar New Year in 2026" /&gt;&lt;p&gt;After the Lunar New Year in 2026, I’d like to record the second time I&amp;rsquo;ve taken my puppy back to my hometown and what has been happening in my life. When I got off work on February 13, I didn’t go back to my hometown immediately. I wanted to clean my house, and I had an English class on Saturday, so I wanted to finish everything before going back to my hometown.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;On Sunday, my mom and a friend drove to Taipei, and I took them to Ootoya for lunch and walked around the area afterward.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="https://yangcj.cc/p/lunar-new-year-in-2026/Ootoya.jpg"
width="4096"
height="3072"
srcset="https://yangcj.cc/p/lunar-new-year-in-2026/Ootoya_hu_334f76448d92be17.jpg 480w, https://yangcj.cc/p/lunar-new-year-in-2026/Ootoya_hu_cbca788ff02e18cb.jpg 1024w"
loading="lazy"
alt="Ootoya"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="133"
data-flex-basis="320px"
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We went back to my house, and then I started packing my things and my puppy’s things, getting ready to go to my hometown. Before that, my puppy had gotten motion sickness last year, so my mom prepared some motion sickness medicine for her. Fortunately, my puppy didn’t get carsick this time. She’s really my best daughter.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="https://yangcj.cc/p/lunar-new-year-in-2026/loubogao-in-the-car.jpg"
width="3072"
height="4096"
srcset="https://yangcj.cc/p/lunar-new-year-in-2026/loubogao-in-the-car_hu_47ab2b7a3f7019ee.jpg 480w, https://yangcj.cc/p/lunar-new-year-in-2026/loubogao-in-the-car_hu_3749020bee2deaf6.jpg 1024w"
loading="lazy"
alt="My puppy was In the Car"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="75"
data-flex-basis="180px"
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We arrived in my hometown at about 7:00 p.m. I unpacked and got some water for my puppy, and then we had lamb hot pot together for dinner. Lamb hot pot is a traditional specialty from my hometown, so this time I took it back to Taipei to share with my friends.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="https://yangcj.cc/p/lunar-new-year-in-2026/lamb-hot-pot.jpg"
width="3072"
height="4096"
srcset="https://yangcj.cc/p/lunar-new-year-in-2026/lamb-hot-pot_hu_9253a3b2fd0262fe.jpg 480w, https://yangcj.cc/p/lunar-new-year-in-2026/lamb-hot-pot_hu_12eb1816a0da1c60.jpg 1024w"
loading="lazy"
alt="Lamb Hot Pot"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="75"
data-flex-basis="180px"
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;My puppy was still timid this time because she was afraid of my mom’s puppies. When we had dinner, she would hide behind me every time. However, I thought she was so cute.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="https://yangcj.cc/p/lunar-new-year-in-2026/loubogao-hide-behind-me.jpg"
width="4928"
height="6560"
srcset="https://yangcj.cc/p/lunar-new-year-in-2026/loubogao-hide-behind-me_hu_b6eb910f2c7f36c4.jpg 480w, https://yangcj.cc/p/lunar-new-year-in-2026/loubogao-hide-behind-me_hu_fadce7cb6a172792.jpg 1024w"
loading="lazy"
alt="My puppy hide behind me"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="75"
data-flex-basis="180px"
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;After dinner, I took my puppy to my room and prepared dinner for her. Then I found my CDs and started ripping all of them to FLAC format and listening to them using Roon.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="https://yangcj.cc/p/lunar-new-year-in-2026/my-cds.jpg"
width="1080"
height="1920"
srcset="https://yangcj.cc/p/lunar-new-year-in-2026/my-cds_hu_d2733c5c10213e07.jpg 480w, https://yangcj.cc/p/lunar-new-year-in-2026/my-cds_hu_b26318d5f55ba0b1.jpg 1024w"
loading="lazy"
alt="My CDs"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="56"
data-flex-basis="135px"
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;During the process, I found many songs that I had not listened to for a long time. They brought back many memories, so I decided to keep them as well.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="https://yangcj.cc/p/lunar-new-year-in-2026/roon.png"
width="1919"
height="1032"
srcset="https://yangcj.cc/p/lunar-new-year-in-2026/roon_hu_63c53a017fceec35.png 480w, https://yangcj.cc/p/lunar-new-year-in-2026/roon_hu_56be4184f8fae14f.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
alt="Roon"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="185"
data-flex-basis="446px"
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;My puppy and I sleplt together every night. My puppy looked so cute sleeping on the bed. Before I knew it, having her sleep next to me made me feel calm and safe.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="https://yangcj.cc/p/lunar-new-year-in-2026/lobogao-slept.jpg"
width="3060"
height="4080"
srcset="https://yangcj.cc/p/lunar-new-year-in-2026/lobogao-slept_hu_d1ab7c352103cc74.jpg 480w, https://yangcj.cc/p/lunar-new-year-in-2026/lobogao-slept_hu_84e0c045cea001ee.jpg 1024w"
loading="lazy"
alt="My puppy Slept"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="75"
data-flex-basis="180px"
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I was with my family every day until I came back to Taipei. Actually, I also did a lot of things during this holiday, but above all, these are my most precious memories.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Installing Debian Linux Distribution</title><link>https://yangcj.cc/p/installing-debian-linux/</link><pubDate>Sat, 07 Feb 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://yangcj.cc/p/installing-debian-linux/</guid><description>&lt;img src="https://yangcj.cc/p/installing-debian-linux/banner.jpg" alt="Featured image of post Installing Debian Linux Distribution" /&gt;&lt;p&gt;Debian is my favorite Linux distribution. I installed it on my retired PC and use it as my server OS. I have used Debian for over a decade. It is free, open, and very stable. I use it to practice build many server, such as DNS, NAT, SMB, Website, Database, and so on.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In 2026, I will rewrite an article documenting my Debian usage. The first section will describe the process of installing Debian, and then I will write more articles about how to use Debian to set up various types of servers.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Now, I&amp;rsquo;m going to show you how to install Debian with VirtualBox. Here we go!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We need to get the Debian installation media from the official website first. I am providing the &lt;a class="link" href="https://www.debian.org/CD/http-ftp/index.en.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;link&lt;/a&gt;, and you can click it to download.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="https://yangcj.cc/p/installing-debian-linux/debian-official-website.png"
width="1920"
height="986"
srcset="https://yangcj.cc/p/installing-debian-linux/debian-official-website_hu_93506d980ad1c6e1.png 480w, https://yangcj.cc/p/installing-debian-linux/debian-official-website_hu_274703d2c6d9c016.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
alt="Debian Official Website"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="194"
data-flex-basis="467px"
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;After downloading the installation media, open VirtualBox. We need to create a virtual machine. At this step, we do not need “Proceed with Unattended Installation,” so uncheck the box.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="https://yangcj.cc/p/installing-debian-linux/setting-virtualbox-1.png"
width="960"
height="749"
srcset="https://yangcj.cc/p/installing-debian-linux/setting-virtualbox-1_hu_fea1563713c5dd01.png 480w, https://yangcj.cc/p/installing-debian-linux/setting-virtualbox-1_hu_a48d7a07041ad52e.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
alt="Vitual Box"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="128"
data-flex-basis="307px"
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Next, configure the virtual hardware. I recommend increasing the disk size because we will need enough space to set up various types of servers.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="https://yangcj.cc/p/installing-debian-linux/setting-virtualbox-2.png"
width="960"
height="749"
srcset="https://yangcj.cc/p/installing-debian-linux/setting-virtualbox-2_hu_f434cf25761b4980.png 480w, https://yangcj.cc/p/installing-debian-linux/setting-virtualbox-2_hu_f6856075d29582dd.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
alt="Vitual Box"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="128"
data-flex-basis="307px"
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Click Finish to complete the creation of the virtual machine.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="https://yangcj.cc/p/installing-debian-linux/setting-virtualbox-3.png"
width="960"
height="749"
srcset="https://yangcj.cc/p/installing-debian-linux/setting-virtualbox-3_hu_d0fb6fe2273ce3bc.png 480w, https://yangcj.cc/p/installing-debian-linux/setting-virtualbox-3_hu_bdfff7eb09daeef2.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
alt="Vitual Box"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="128"
data-flex-basis="307px"
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Now everything is ready, and we can begin installing Debian.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="https://yangcj.cc/p/installing-debian-linux/setting-virtualbox-4.png"
width="960"
height="749"
srcset="https://yangcj.cc/p/installing-debian-linux/setting-virtualbox-4_hu_7d4e4ad84bd6e6fd.png 480w, https://yangcj.cc/p/installing-debian-linux/setting-virtualbox-4_hu_85252e419fbe8649.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
alt="Vitual Box"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="128"
data-flex-basis="307px"
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Click Start to power on the virtual machine, then select Install because I prefer using the text‑based installer.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="https://yangcj.cc/p/installing-debian-linux/debian-installed-1.png"
width="1920"
height="1031"
srcset="https://yangcj.cc/p/installing-debian-linux/debian-installed-1_hu_386ef759cf93e655.png 480w, https://yangcj.cc/p/installing-debian-linux/debian-installed-1_hu_bbca502e082b1842.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
alt="Debian"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="186"
data-flex-basis="446px"
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Select a language, and choose English.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="https://yangcj.cc/p/installing-debian-linux/debian-installed-2.png"
width="800"
height="684"
srcset="https://yangcj.cc/p/installing-debian-linux/debian-installed-2_hu_792929eaab4739ef.png 480w, https://yangcj.cc/p/installing-debian-linux/debian-installed-2_hu_36ee3b4ff51c856b.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
alt="Debian"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="116"
data-flex-basis="280px"
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Select your location, and choose Taiwan.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="https://yangcj.cc/p/installing-debian-linux/debian-installed-3.png"
width="800"
height="684"
srcset="https://yangcj.cc/p/installing-debian-linux/debian-installed-3_hu_7e6db089300ed89a.png 480w, https://yangcj.cc/p/installing-debian-linux/debian-installed-3_hu_8c3efa31a475e9fc.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
alt="Debian"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="116"
data-flex-basis="280px"
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Configure locales, and choose United States.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="https://yangcj.cc/p/installing-debian-linux/debian-installed-4.png"
width="800"
height="684"
srcset="https://yangcj.cc/p/installing-debian-linux/debian-installed-4_hu_c586844cd70bf279.png 480w, https://yangcj.cc/p/installing-debian-linux/debian-installed-4_hu_18ea7f995b701bbf.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
alt="Debian"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="116"
data-flex-basis="280px"
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Configure the keyboard, and choose American English.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="https://yangcj.cc/p/installing-debian-linux/debian-installed-5.png"
width="800"
height="684"
srcset="https://yangcj.cc/p/installing-debian-linux/debian-installed-5_hu_896b8944c499bcbc.png 480w, https://yangcj.cc/p/installing-debian-linux/debian-installed-5_hu_83cb60df6cb82f71.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
alt="Debian"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="116"
data-flex-basis="280px"
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Configure the network, then enter a hostname.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="https://yangcj.cc/p/installing-debian-linux/debian-installed-6.png"
width="800"
height="684"
srcset="https://yangcj.cc/p/installing-debian-linux/debian-installed-6_hu_ed36bb56e5020d35.png 480w, https://yangcj.cc/p/installing-debian-linux/debian-installed-6_hu_7246bd20d888156a.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
alt="Debian"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="116"
data-flex-basis="280px"
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Configure the network again, then either leave the domain name blank or enter your own.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="https://yangcj.cc/p/installing-debian-linux/debian-installed-7.png"
width="800"
height="684"
srcset="https://yangcj.cc/p/installing-debian-linux/debian-installed-7_hu_331245ad1fb5accd.png 480w, https://yangcj.cc/p/installing-debian-linux/debian-installed-7_hu_aebf5da06e6cda42.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
alt="Debian"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="116"
data-flex-basis="280px"
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Enter the root password.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="https://yangcj.cc/p/installing-debian-linux/debian-installed-8.png"
width="800"
height="684"
srcset="https://yangcj.cc/p/installing-debian-linux/debian-installed-8_hu_408515005a6b51ab.png 480w, https://yangcj.cc/p/installing-debian-linux/debian-installed-8_hu_4cc3ae4ba77044e7.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
alt="Debian"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="116"
data-flex-basis="280px"
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Re‑enter the root password.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="https://yangcj.cc/p/installing-debian-linux/debian-installed-9.png"
width="800"
height="684"
srcset="https://yangcj.cc/p/installing-debian-linux/debian-installed-9_hu_44f2c9b8f280687.png 480w, https://yangcj.cc/p/installing-debian-linux/debian-installed-9_hu_eae3d99e4dcff478.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
alt="Debian"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="116"
data-flex-basis="280px"
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Enter your full name.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="https://yangcj.cc/p/installing-debian-linux/debian-installed-10.png"
width="800"
height="684"
srcset="https://yangcj.cc/p/installing-debian-linux/debian-installed-10_hu_ddda0ab6c9c17c1b.png 480w, https://yangcj.cc/p/installing-debian-linux/debian-installed-10_hu_1cb1dc3874c4d32e.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
alt="Debian"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="116"
data-flex-basis="280px"
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Enter your username.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="https://yangcj.cc/p/installing-debian-linux/debian-installed-11.png"
width="800"
height="684"
srcset="https://yangcj.cc/p/installing-debian-linux/debian-installed-11_hu_a3a6c493a7521053.png 480w, https://yangcj.cc/p/installing-debian-linux/debian-installed-11_hu_27bd9afbd09ae06d.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
alt="Debian"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="116"
data-flex-basis="280px"
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Enter the password for your account.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="https://yangcj.cc/p/installing-debian-linux/debian-installed-12.png"
width="800"
height="684"
srcset="https://yangcj.cc/p/installing-debian-linux/debian-installed-12_hu_8e53dad24deaa2a0.png 480w, https://yangcj.cc/p/installing-debian-linux/debian-installed-12_hu_fda28c992ed5d67c.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
alt="Debian"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="116"
data-flex-basis="280px"
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Re‑enter the password.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="https://yangcj.cc/p/installing-debian-linux/debian-installed-13.png"
width="800"
height="684"
srcset="https://yangcj.cc/p/installing-debian-linux/debian-installed-13_hu_55b677627eabc89c.png 480w, https://yangcj.cc/p/installing-debian-linux/debian-installed-13_hu_e07440ff38b5efb4.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
alt="Debian"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="116"
data-flex-basis="280px"
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Choose Guided – use entire disk.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="https://yangcj.cc/p/installing-debian-linux/debian-installed-14.png"
width="800"
height="684"
srcset="https://yangcj.cc/p/installing-debian-linux/debian-installed-14_hu_348c919afe763d48.png 480w, https://yangcj.cc/p/installing-debian-linux/debian-installed-14_hu_5ae9e98dd270d4a9.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
alt="Debian"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="116"
data-flex-basis="280px"
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Press Enter to continue.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="https://yangcj.cc/p/installing-debian-linux/debian-installed-15.png"
width="800"
height="684"
srcset="https://yangcj.cc/p/installing-debian-linux/debian-installed-15_hu_1e4fb23eaf83e1f2.png 480w, https://yangcj.cc/p/installing-debian-linux/debian-installed-15_hu_cd0a86770654fc39.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
alt="Debian"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="116"
data-flex-basis="280px"
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Choose All files in one partition (recommended for new users).&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="https://yangcj.cc/p/installing-debian-linux/debian-installed-16.png"
width="800"
height="684"
srcset="https://yangcj.cc/p/installing-debian-linux/debian-installed-16_hu_307a0e7851e24a64.png 480w, https://yangcj.cc/p/installing-debian-linux/debian-installed-16_hu_efc38787e919d88.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
alt="Debian"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="116"
data-flex-basis="280px"
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Choose Finish partitioning and write changes to disk.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="https://yangcj.cc/p/installing-debian-linux/debian-installed-17.png"
width="800"
height="684"
srcset="https://yangcj.cc/p/installing-debian-linux/debian-installed-17_hu_35ba1e75cc1d3a43.png 480w, https://yangcj.cc/p/installing-debian-linux/debian-installed-17_hu_36a2b024f6e2c3a6.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
alt="Debian"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="116"
data-flex-basis="280px"
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Choose Yes.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="https://yangcj.cc/p/installing-debian-linux/debian-installed-18.png"
width="800"
height="684"
srcset="https://yangcj.cc/p/installing-debian-linux/debian-installed-18_hu_1fc2de8f7b728d9d.png 480w, https://yangcj.cc/p/installing-debian-linux/debian-installed-18_hu_dbd66b4cfffead75.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
alt="Debian"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="116"
data-flex-basis="280px"
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Choose No when asked to scan extra installation media.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="https://yangcj.cc/p/installing-debian-linux/debian-installed-19.png"
width="800"
height="684"
srcset="https://yangcj.cc/p/installing-debian-linux/debian-installed-19_hu_a5d560a98fe93fa3.png 480w, https://yangcj.cc/p/installing-debian-linux/debian-installed-19_hu_5641bf43a66a80bb.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
alt="Debian"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="116"
data-flex-basis="280px"
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Choose Yes to use a network mirror.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="https://yangcj.cc/p/installing-debian-linux/debian-installed-20.png"
width="800"
height="684"
srcset="https://yangcj.cc/p/installing-debian-linux/debian-installed-20_hu_a4247ee0613fb725.png 480w, https://yangcj.cc/p/installing-debian-linux/debian-installed-20_hu_de16a225279b50c5.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
alt="Debian"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="116"
data-flex-basis="280px"
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Choose Taiwan.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="https://yangcj.cc/p/installing-debian-linux/debian-installed-21.png"
width="800"
height="684"
srcset="https://yangcj.cc/p/installing-debian-linux/debian-installed-21_hu_62fe422858ccf53.png 480w, https://yangcj.cc/p/installing-debian-linux/debian-installed-21_hu_eb80173e63f1cf09.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
alt="Debian"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="116"
data-flex-basis="280px"
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Choose any mirror you prefer.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="https://yangcj.cc/p/installing-debian-linux/debian-installed-22.png"
width="800"
height="684"
srcset="https://yangcj.cc/p/installing-debian-linux/debian-installed-22_hu_f0b6410e4a7893de.png 480w, https://yangcj.cc/p/installing-debian-linux/debian-installed-22_hu_37edb231752f3a29.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
alt="Debian"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="116"
data-flex-basis="280px"
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Leave the proxy field blank.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="https://yangcj.cc/p/installing-debian-linux/debian-installed-23.png"
width="800"
height="684"
srcset="https://yangcj.cc/p/installing-debian-linux/debian-installed-23_hu_b10974b9b2e846f8.png 480w, https://yangcj.cc/p/installing-debian-linux/debian-installed-23_hu_2589f67003859c9e.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
alt="Debian"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="116"
data-flex-basis="280px"
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For popularity‑contest, choose No.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="https://yangcj.cc/p/installing-debian-linux/debian-installed-24.png"
width="800"
height="684"
srcset="https://yangcj.cc/p/installing-debian-linux/debian-installed-24_hu_1a210cb7f061738e.png 480w, https://yangcj.cc/p/installing-debian-linux/debian-installed-24_hu_e0ce2af7325ab79c.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
alt="Debian"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="116"
data-flex-basis="280px"
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For software selection, choose SSH Server and standard system utilities.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="https://yangcj.cc/p/installing-debian-linux/debian-installed-25.png"
width="800"
height="684"
srcset="https://yangcj.cc/p/installing-debian-linux/debian-installed-25_hu_af7ee00216f92db5.png 480w, https://yangcj.cc/p/installing-debian-linux/debian-installed-25_hu_6e065fb03245a735.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
alt="Debian"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="116"
data-flex-basis="280px"
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For GRUB installation, choose Yes.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="https://yangcj.cc/p/installing-debian-linux/debian-installed-26.png"
width="800"
height="684"
srcset="https://yangcj.cc/p/installing-debian-linux/debian-installed-26_hu_fc42f731b4c6e06.png 480w, https://yangcj.cc/p/installing-debian-linux/debian-installed-26_hu_8bfa90c912153d6a.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
alt="Debian"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="116"
data-flex-basis="280px"
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Select /dev/sda.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="https://yangcj.cc/p/installing-debian-linux/debian-installed-27.png"
width="800"
height="684"
srcset="https://yangcj.cc/p/installing-debian-linux/debian-installed-27_hu_aa1bfffe03afbdba.png 480w, https://yangcj.cc/p/installing-debian-linux/debian-installed-27_hu_2124a45f3069e7f1.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
alt="Debian"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="116"
data-flex-basis="280px"
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Choose Continue to reboot.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="https://yangcj.cc/p/installing-debian-linux/debian-installed-28.png"
width="800"
height="684"
srcset="https://yangcj.cc/p/installing-debian-linux/debian-installed-28_hu_83f6c108ee91ddb9.png 480w, https://yangcj.cc/p/installing-debian-linux/debian-installed-28_hu_7c98bf2ce11964b2.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
alt="Debian"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="116"
data-flex-basis="280px"
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Now you have a working Debian virtual machine.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="https://yangcj.cc/p/installing-debian-linux/debian-installed-29.png"
width="1279"
height="883"
srcset="https://yangcj.cc/p/installing-debian-linux/debian-installed-29_hu_efae1ca0ad2ad007.png 480w, https://yangcj.cc/p/installing-debian-linux/debian-installed-29_hu_1b311c20c1c354d8.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
alt="Debian"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="144"
data-flex-basis="347px"
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I will share more Debian‑related articles in the future.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>My Broken NAS in 2026</title><link>https://yangcj.cc/p/my-broken-nas-in-2026/</link><pubDate>Sat, 31 Jan 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://yangcj.cc/p/my-broken-nas-in-2026/</guid><description>&lt;img src="https://yangcj.cc/p/my-broken-nas-in-2026/banner.jpg" alt="Featured image of post My Broken NAS in 2026" /&gt;&lt;p&gt;Oh my God. I cannot believe that my first article is about my broken NAS in 2026. When I was still living in my hometown, I bought a Synology NAS. Synology NAS devices are very convenient and stable. They offer many applications that allow me to access my documents and photos, and even build virtual machines from anywhere. After that, I canceled all of my cloud storage subscriptions.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Back then, I bought a 4‑bay NAS and used RAID 5 to protect my data. If one hard disk failed, I could simply replace it and the system would automatically rebuild the data. But for the first time, the failure wasn’t the hard disk — it was the machine itself. So I just ended up buying a new one.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="https://yangcj.cc/p/my-broken-nas-in-2026/DS918&amp;#43;.JPEG"
width="1280"
height="1707"
srcset="https://yangcj.cc/p/my-broken-nas-in-2026/DS918&amp;#43;_hu_e45d925c22c3e00a.JPEG 480w, https://yangcj.cc/p/my-broken-nas-in-2026/DS918&amp;#43;_hu_bf9e30c94616e11b.JPEG 1024w"
loading="lazy"
alt="DS918&amp;#43;"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="74"
data-flex-basis="179px"
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Fortunately, I’m used to setting up servers with my retired PCs, and I also have scheduled backups for my NAS data. When I found it was broken, I immediately backed up my backup NAS data from the server to another hard disk, and then I bought a new one. This time, I decided to go with a 2‑bay NAS because I don’t need that much storage space.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="https://yangcj.cc/p/my-broken-nas-in-2026/DS225&amp;#43;.JPEG"
width="1280"
height="1707"
srcset="https://yangcj.cc/p/my-broken-nas-in-2026/DS225&amp;#43;_hu_acedd846afb0c44e.JPEG 480w, https://yangcj.cc/p/my-broken-nas-in-2026/DS225&amp;#43;_hu_96276a0815afd364.JPEG 1024w"
loading="lazy"
alt="DS225&amp;#43;"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="74"
data-flex-basis="179px"
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Now all my NAS data has been recovered, and the new NAS is running very smoothly. I can use it just like before, and I hope it will last for a long time.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Welcome to My Family</title><link>https://yangcj.cc/p/welcome-to-my-life/</link><pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://yangcj.cc/p/welcome-to-my-life/</guid><description>&lt;img src="https://yangcj.cc/p/welcome-to-my-life/banner.jpg" alt="Featured image of post Welcome to My Family" /&gt;&lt;p&gt;After I left IBM, the first thing I wanted to do was get my life back. So I decided to get a puppy. I started looking on different websites, and eventually I found one on &lt;a class="link" href="https://cute-puppy.com.tw/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;乖乖狗寵物家&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;When I first saw her, I felt that she was incredibly adorable, and she had a very special fur color. I knew it was her at that moment. I immediately sent a message to the shop and made a reservation to visit her. I wanted to take her home as soon as possible.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="https://yangcj.cc/p/welcome-to-my-life/my-puppy-img-01.jpg"
width="2027"
height="2225"
srcset="https://yangcj.cc/p/welcome-to-my-life/my-puppy-img-01_hu_5efbaff6ff56eb5a.jpg 480w, https://yangcj.cc/p/welcome-to-my-life/my-puppy-img-01_hu_855a610e49c83182.jpg 1024w"
loading="lazy"
alt="My Puppy"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="91"
data-flex-basis="218px"
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;That day, I really looked forward to seeing her. When it was time, I took an Uber, feeling very happy. After about 30 minutes, I arrived at the shop. As soon as I went in, the owner put her on the ground. She was full of energy and kept following me everywhere, even chewing on my pants. It seemed like she knew I was there to take her home. I knew she was the best encounter of my life. Then I started handling the paperwork. However, I didn’t have any dog supplies at home. Fortunately, the shop also sold some basic pet supplies, so I bought them there right away.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="https://yangcj.cc/p/welcome-to-my-life/dog-supplies.jpg"
width="3072"
height="4096"
srcset="https://yangcj.cc/p/welcome-to-my-life/dog-supplies_hu_8f4c8fea02e81e23.jpg 480w, https://yangcj.cc/p/welcome-to-my-life/dog-supplies_hu_f7afd020311ecaf7.jpg 1024w"
loading="lazy"
alt="Dog Supplies"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="75"
data-flex-basis="180px"
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;When we got home, I opened the box and let her see her new home. Then I started setting up her space. After that, I put her in her place, and I was very surprised because she seemed to know this was her home. She immediately wanted to explore everywhere in the house.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="https://yangcj.cc/p/welcome-to-my-life/my-puppy-img-02.jpg"
width="3072"
height="4096"
srcset="https://yangcj.cc/p/welcome-to-my-life/my-puppy-img-02_hu_2caab5551618e1ef.jpg 480w, https://yangcj.cc/p/welcome-to-my-life/my-puppy-img-02_hu_fa7ca252ae0f897.jpg 1024w"
loading="lazy"
alt="My Puppy"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="75"
data-flex-basis="180px"
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;She fit in very well in her new home. After playing for a while, she fell asleep comfortably in her place. The place was temporary, and I planned to prepare a better one for her.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="https://yangcj.cc/p/welcome-to-my-life/my-puppy-img-03.jpg"
width="3072"
height="4096"
srcset="https://yangcj.cc/p/welcome-to-my-life/my-puppy-img-03_hu_d2da2e09bd29afdc.jpg 480w, https://yangcj.cc/p/welcome-to-my-life/my-puppy-img-03_hu_d9eec77f12cba8df.jpg 1024w"
loading="lazy"
alt="My Puppy"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="75"
data-flex-basis="180px"
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In the end, I took her home, which was a lifelong promise I made to her. I was truly grateful that she became part of my life. From that moment on, we began our journey together.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>